  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D Action</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/43313b90c738d3585af9cd20e3169ba2.poster.avif?t=1601638092\" width=452 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/43313b90c738d3585af9cd20e3169ba2.webm?t=1601638092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/43313b90c738d3585af9cd20e3169ba2.mp4?t=1601638092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> - Basic action manipulation such as double jump, air attack, and combo attacks.<br> - Some physical is required.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stages</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/084cf93d8a6a73c19f5a6681764a7faa.poster.avif?t=1601638092\" width=752 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/084cf93d8a6a73c19f5a6681764a7faa.webm?t=1601638092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/084cf93d8a6a73c19f5a6681764a7faa.mp4?t=1601638092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> - Clear the first to ninth floors and boss, you clear the stage.<br> - Total 6 stages are ready and you can watch the Ending.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill Combination</h2> - Clearing stage unlocks more skills you can choose. Find skill combinations that suit you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/982b93ce7f29bb3489a62ac90eddcb09.avif?t=1601638092\" width=684 height=384 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite Feature</h2> - Skills and items disappear after the end of each stages.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrades</h2> - You can permanently upgrade the player through the jewels you have acquired.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177080/extras/e6ae26f6b13edfb81ba2aa2a2ec03ab3.avif?t=1601638092\" width=684 height=370 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlocks</h2>Clearing some stage unlocks new characters.<br>Clearing some Silver Room unlocks new movement skills.<br>Clearing some Gold Room unlocks new passives.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Attack</h2> - Don't waste even a second! No matter what, kill them faster, you get more items.",
